Lines Store" href="http://www.pagelines.com/store/" target="_blank">PageLines Store</a>, followed by a monthly email newsletter which showcases the best of the best for the month.</p>\n<p>Because you want the latest and greatest add-ons for your website, here&#8217;s a handy little recap of what&#8217;s new in the PageLines Store. Don&#8217;t receive the PageLines email newsletter? <a title="Sign up for the PageLines Newsletter" href="http://bit.ly/PL-Newsletter" target="_blank">Sign up now</a> and never miss a thing!</p>\n<p><a title="View the Doppelganger Bar add-on" href="http://www.pagelines.com/store/sections/doppelganger-bar/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9686" alt="doppelganger bar" src="http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/doppelganger.png" width="644" height="333" /></a></p>\n<h2>Doppelgänger Bar</h2>\n<p>Doppelgänger Bar is an insanely powerful sidebar section meant to replace or enhance your sidebars. Display different sidebars on different pages, add responsive sidebars to the header, add some more in the footer, make a whole page out of just sidebars &#8211; the possibilities are endless!</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-primary" title="Doppelganger Bar" href="http://www.pagelines.com/store/sections/doppelganger-bar/" target="_blank">Overview</a> <a class="btn" title="Doppelganger Bar" href="http://evanmattson.pagelines.me/sections/doppelganger-bar/" target="_blank">Demo</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><a title="View the Social Counter add-on" href="http://www.pagelines.com/store/sections/social-counter/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9688" alt="social counter" src="http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/social_counter.png" width="644" height="321" /></a></p>\n<h2>Social Counter</h2>\n<p>The Social Counter section lets you show off your social media street cred like a boss. Display follower numbers for Facebook, Twitter, Dribble, RSS, YouTube, Instagram, and WordPress with multiple layout and color options.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-primary" title="Social Counter" href="http://www.pagelines.com/store/sections/social-counter/" target="_blank">Overview</a> <a class="btn" title="Social Counter" href="http://adammunns.com/social-counter" target="_blank">Demo</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><a title="View the Hooker plugin" href="http://www.pagelines.com/store/plugins/hooker/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9689" alt="hooker plugin" src="http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hooker_email.png" width="644" height="328" /></a></p>\n<h2>Hooker</h2>\n<p>Finally.. the tool you have been dreaming about! With this plugin you can add HTML, JavaScript, and PHP <em>anywhere</em> on your website using built-in PageLines Hooks. Just select a hook from the dropdown box, add custom code, and click save. Too easy!</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-primary" title="Hooker" href="http://www.pagelines.com/store/plugins/hooker/" target="_blank">Overview</a> <a class="btn" title="Hooker" href="http://www.pagelines.com/plus/" target="_blank">Now FREE with Plus</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Have a great idea for a new section or plugin? <a href="http://www.pagelines.com/contact/" title="Contact us" target="_blank">Let us know</a>!</strong></p>\n<div id="wpcr_respond_1"></div><p>The post <a href="http://www.pagelines.com/pagelines-store-your-march-update/">PageLines Store: Your March Update</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.pagelines.com">PageLines</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:64:"http://www.pagelines.com/pagelines-store-your-march-update/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"5";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:1