0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"Stefan";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2645:"<p>We value innovation and ease-of-use at PageLines and we are constantly looking for ways to improve the products we release, the impressions we leave and most importantly, the experiences we create. We&#8217;ve been working on an amazing new support center, and we want you to check it out.</p>\n<p>We are pleased to announce the new <a href="http://support.pagelines.me">PageLines Support Center</a>. It combines a new interface with the PageLines ease-of-use, creating the best experience for our clients. The new system assists all PageLines users in achieving their goals by delivering high-quality, hand-crafted resources right at their fingertips.</p>\n<div class="btn-group">\n<a class="btn" href="http://support.pagelines.me/docs">Documentation</a>\n<a class="btn" href="http://www.pagelines.com/forum">Support Forum</a>\n<a class="btn" href="http://support.pagelines.me/helpdesk">HelpDesk</a>\n<a class="btn" href="http://pagelines.com/translate/projects/pagelines-framework">Translation Center</a>\n<a class="btn" href="http://www.pagelines.com/forum/tracdown">Tracker</a>\n<a class="btn" href="http://www.pagelines.com/pros">Pros</a>\n</div>\n<p>The Support Center has been built exclusively on the PageLines Framework, offering a central state-of-the-art solution to PageLines users, from absolute beginners to developers. It offers quick access to the completely revamped <a href="http://support.pagelines.me/docs"><em>PageLines Documentation</em></a>, <a href="http://www.pagelines.com/forum"><em>Technical Support Forum</em></a>, <em><a href="http://support.pagelines.me/helpdesk">Help Desk</a></em> and more, covering every aspect of <em>the</em> PageLines Experience.</p>\n<p>The end result is a centralized support resource that is beautiful and streamlined to offer clients faster access to valuable information.</p>\n<p>Try the <a href="http://support.pagelines.me">PageLines Support Center</a>. We hope you find it amazing.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 15px; box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px 3px #C0C0C0;" href="http://support.pagelines.me"><strong><em class="icon-pagelines"> </em>PageLines Support Center</strong></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Special thanks go out to Danny (main support center contributor), </em></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Catrina (graphics and contributions), Jenny and Stefan (spellchecking)</em></p>\n<div id="wpcr_respond_1"></div><p>The post <a href="http://www.pagelines.com/introducing-the-new-pagelines-support-center/">Introducing the PageLines Support Center</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.pagelines.com">PageLines</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"http://www.pagelines.com/introducing-the-new-pagelines-support-center/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"4";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:1:{s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:3:"url";s:96:"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Support-Center-_-PageLines-final-130x130.png";s:5:"width";s:3:"130";s:6:"height";s:3:"130";s:6:"medium";s:5:"image";s:4:"type";s:9:"image/png";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_ex